    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone prioritizing reliable transportation over a perfect appearance. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor dings on the door panels, and clear coat fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible wear and some staining from regular use, and the plastic trim has some scuffing. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it may require some minor cosmetic attention if you prefer a sharper look. It is a solid, dependable driver that provides great value for those looking for a functional commute.",
