    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014it\u2019s completely spotless inside and out, and it drives like a dream. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new and ready for a new home, you\u2019ve found it. Come by and take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
