    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade vehicle that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Finished in a stunning, deep-gloss metallic paint that has been professionally ceramic coated, the exterior is absolutely flawless\u2014free of any stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats are supple with zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or rattles. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history at authorized dealerships and stored in a climate-controlled garage its entire life. It drives tight and responsive, with smooth power delivery and crisp shifts. Included are both original keys, all owner's manuals, and a clean title. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle is the benchmark.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
