      "description": "Hey friends! I'm parting ways with my absolute dream of a car and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014it\u2019s seriously flawless inside and out. It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person. I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
