    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with its signature 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a surgical maintenance history, including preventative rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high lateral G-loads. The 6-speed manual gearbox remains tight with factory-spec throw precision, paired with a variable M-differential lock for optimal power delivery. The Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system is fully functional, providing a seamless transition between compliant street use and track-ready stiffness. No cosmetic blemishes or mechanical deviations from OEM specifications; this is a pure, turn-key investment for the serious driver.",
